lead_paragraph: Olympians Carmelita Jeter and Nick Symmonds have withdrawn from the U.S. athletics trials for the Rio Olympics with injuries, they said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Athletics: Injured Jeter, Symmonds to Miss U.S. Olympic Trials
